node.text:
💪 @trevormcclung battled his way through the final brackets of the #RedBullParisConquest and came out on top! 
Watch the recap of the Final now playing on our YouTube. Link in bio. 📺
#skate #skateboarding #skatecontest #redbullskate

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Red Bull Skateboarding on August 18, 2021 tagging @trevormcclung, @etniesskateboarding, and @etnies. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
🏆Congrats to @trevormcclung & @leticiabufoni on winning the first  #RedBullParisConquest !! The Final was heated with skaters battling it out head to head to advance to the next round. If you missed it live you can hit the link in our bio to watch the Men's & Women's Final! 

🥇 @leticiabufoni 
🥈 @aori_nishimura 
🥉 @charlotte_hym 

🥇 @trevormcclung 
🥈 @aureliengiraud 
🥉 @vincentmilou
